name: The MetaScream. Working Layer 1: The Scream.
description: The Meta Project by Meta P starts with an open call for artists, invited to take part in the first collective artwork of the collection. This is the first Working Layer to generate your new artwork (only 88 entries available). It's "The Scream" by Edvard Munch (Courtesy of National Gallery, Oslo). Grab your and fill this form to take part in the NFT Revolution: https://forms.gle/BQymK3qozUUjbx4g8 You might be chosen to work together with renowned artists to create the first multi-artist, multi-layered, cross time-space NFT artwork.
